com.enterprise_architecture.essential.widgets
Class ReportServiceClient

java.lang.Object
  com.enterprise_architecture.essential.widgets.ReportServiceClient

public class ReportServiceClient
extends java.lang.Object

Client for the EAS Architecture Reporting Service. Uses a SwingWorker thread to make the request in a separate thread whilst allowing the User Interface tab, EASReportTab to continue.
Used by the EasReportTab

Since:
v1.0
Version:
2.0 - Added progress tracking via a listener pattern
, 1.3 - Remove sending of graph images to Viewer
, 1.2 - Send GraphWidget images to Viewer
Author:
Jonathan W. Carter
See Also:
EasReportTab
